Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
At Padadaz, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use our app.
2. Information We Collect
We collect certain information automatically when you use the app, including device information, usage data, and app activity data. This information is collected using Firebase Analytics and Amplitude.
3. How We Use Your Information
We use the data collected to:
Improve our app's performance and user experience.
Understand user behavior and preferences.
Communicate with you about the app, updates, and new features.
4. Sharing Your Information
We do not share your personal data with third parties except for the services required to operate and analyze the app (Firebase Analytics and Amplitude).
5. Data Security
We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. We have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to request access to the data we hold about you, request correction of any inaccuracies, and request deletion of your data. Please contact
support@padadaz.com
.
7. Changes to This Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at
support@padadaz.com
.